HEADWORD: Dactyliography
<hw>Dac*tyl`i*og"ra*phy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>dakty`lios</grk> finger ring + <ets>-graphy</ets>.]</ety>
<fld>(Fine Arts)</fld> <sd>(a)</sd> <def>The art of writing or engraving
upon gems.</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>In general, the literature or history
of the art.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

